    /// `.link`-attributed run. Cell opens via `NSWorkspace.shared.open`.
    case openURL(URL)
    /// User-bubble chevron. Cell forwards to
    /// `Transcript2Coordinator.requestUserBubbleSheet(id:)` (the
    /// block id lives on the cell, not the layout).
